  "detailed_description": "Paintey is a freeform do whatever you want painting simulator!<br>You can paint everything from your face to the entire environment.<br><br><strong>Key features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Paint all the things!<br></li><li>Paint balloons!<br></li><li>Googly eyes to stick onto anything!<br></li><li>An innovative (Optional) climbing locomotion system!<br></li><li>Birds!<br></li><li>Twitch chat integration! - Optionally spawns users from your twitch chat into the game.</li></ul><br><strong>Coming soon:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>More levels<br></li><li>More interactivity overall<br></li><li>Multiplayer!<br></li><li>Time trial mode?</li></ul><br>Paintey does not have any sort of predefined goals, you just have fun and mess around!",
  "about_the_game": "Paintey is a freeform do whatever you want painting simulator!<br>You can paint everything from your face to the entire environment.<br><br><strong>Key features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Paint all the things!<br></li><li>Paint balloons!<br></li><li>Googly eyes to stick onto anything!<br></li><li>An innovative (Optional) climbing locomotion system!<br></li><li>Birds!<br></li><li>Twitch chat integration! - Optionally spawns users from your twitch chat into the game.</li></ul><br><strong>Coming soon:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>More levels<br></li><li>More interactivity overall<br></li><li>Multiplayer!<br></li><li>Time trial mode?</li></ul><br>Paintey does not have any sort of predefined goals, you just have fun and mess around!",
